No. 2 Silapathar Block Village

The No. 2 Silapathar Block village is located in Sissibargaon taluka of Dhemaji in Assam, India. The census code of this vill is 288887. The total geographical area of No. 2 Silapathar Block village is 631 Hectares / 0.63 KM2. The nearest police station is located in Sissibargaon tahsil.
